query: SELECT c.id, c.date, a.name as artist, v.name as venue, v.city FROM concerts c JOIN artists a ON c.artist_id = a.id JOIN venues v ON c.venue_id = v.id WHERE v.name LIKE '%Temple%' ORDER BY c.date DESC LIMIT 5;
